<br>
Have we all lost this little thing called patience?  It's a freaking game.  If they say they're gonna make us a bit more group friendly, then wait and see what it is.  And if verant went belly up tomorrow and the game went away, you'd find another game or possibly go outside and get some fresh air and some color on your pasty white skin from being locked in your bedroom for days at a time without sleep.<br>
<br>
Sorry, vent over..had to be done :v)<br>
